{"tid":2305070,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"今年畢業 同男朋友要求想要花/小公仔到時影相+當紀念係咪好過份","createTime":"2020-11-29T10:27:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T11:49:57.000Z","uid":360993,"like":13,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0bde4c472556f61fb748ccfbd63058ac75841b52","tid":2305070,"uid":360993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T10:27:01.000Z","msg":"話說上個月終於畢業<br />\n雖然網上搞 但d人都去左學校到影相<br />\n見到人人手上都有公仔/花 我就咩都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/nap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/nap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明已經早多兩星期同男朋友講想要<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但佢最後都冇買<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話好浪費錢 買黎冇咩用<br />\n<br />\n想問下大家我呢個要求係咪好過份<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一生人第一次畢業<br />\n其實我只係想要一份細細地都ok <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然我知唔應該隨波逐流<br />\n但唔知點解見到人人都有自己冇個感覺好差<br />\n最後我都係問人借來影一影<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由細到大其實今次係第一次畢業 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/nap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪我睇得太重<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c22b7c66fe498ab928b5f47a0cb63f295393905b","tid":2305070,"uid":360993,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T10:27:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢話我太港女 <br />\n唉"},{"pid":"5892fd9931dcdbf8cfc2a7fc88146fbe5f19b4fe","tid":2305070,"uid":360993,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T10:28:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇人"},{"pid":"d2b2a359f7853e14067ecb898cf6445fe59d55bc","tid":2305070,"uid":69289,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-2